"e0dad95a10a444a8b0295d6ca4ee7ad872caf700","tid":1476800,"uid":128600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:18:42.000Z","msg":"水同大氣、食物可以靠科技去克服<br />\n<br />\n但重力同時間距離就暫時冇計<br />\n<br />\n所以月球同火星（未有耐）<br />\n係可以最先考慮既殖民地方<br />\n不過點都係起咗個月球基地先<br />\n再利用月球做大型中轉站去其他地方"},{"pid":"7e53c339f31988d862622be555bf7dddce9bedd2","tid":1476800,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T08:47:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}